quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  19,77,"Afaraayta allathee kafara bi-ayatinawaqala laootayanna malan wawalada"
  19,78,"AttalaAAa alghayba ami ittakhathaAAinda arrahmani AAahda"
  19,79,"Kalla sanaktubu ma yaqooluwanamuddu lahu mina alAAathabi madda"
  19,80,"Wanarithuhu ma yaqoolu waya/teenafarda"
  19,81,"Wattakhathoo min dooni Allahialihatan liyakoonoo lahum AAizza"
  19,82,"Kalla sayakfuroona biAAibadatihimwayakoonoona AAalayhim didda"
  19,83,"Alam tara anna arsalna ashshayateenaAAala alkafireena taozzuhum azza"
  19,84,"Fala taAAjal AAalayhim innamanaAAuddu lahum AAadda"
  19,85,"Yawma nahshuru almuttaqeena ilaarrahmani wafda"
  19,86,"Wanasooqu almujrimeena ila jahannamawirda"
  19,87,"La yamlikoona ashshafaAAatailla mani ittakhatha AAinda arrahmaniAAahda"
  19,88,"Waqaloo ittakhatha arrahmanuwalada"
  19,89,"Laqad ji/tum shay-an idda"
  19,90,"Takadu assamawatuyatafattarna minhu watanshaqqu al-ardu watakhirrualjibalu hadda"
  19,91,"An daAAaw lirrahmaniwalada"
  19,92,"Wama yanbaghee lirrahmanian yattakhitha walada"
  19,93,"In kullu man fee assamawatiwal-ardi illa atee arrahmaniAAabda"
  19,94,"Laqad ahsahum waAAaddahum AAadda"
  19,95,"Wakulluhum ateehi yawma alqiyamatifarda"
